ravensproject

Class RavensObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • ravensproject.RavensObject

  • public class RavensObject
extends java.lang.Object
    A single object in a RavensFigure -- typically, a single shape in a frame, such as a triangle or a circle -- comprised of a list of RavensAttributes.

      • getAttributes

        public java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> getAttributes()
        Returns a HashMap of attributes characterizing this RavensObject. The key for these attributes is the name of the attribute, and the value is the value of the attribute. For example, a filled large square would have attribute pairs "shape:square", "size:large", and "filled:yes".
        Returns:
        a HashMap of name-value attribute pairs.
